---
// What You Get section
---

<section id="what-you-get" class="bg-brand-gray py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <div class="inline-block bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-6">
          The System
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-6">
          Delegating Your Health
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-brand-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          You delegate everything else. This is delegating your health to someone who won't let you off the hook.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefits grid -->
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Benefit 1 -->
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg border border-brand-accent/20 hover:border-brand-accent/50 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3">
            Daily Async Check-ins
          </h3>

          <p class="text-brand-muted mb-4">
            Not calls. Not forms. Quick back-and-forth, same way you already run your team.
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm text-brand-accent font-semibold">
            Built for your calendar, not mine.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefit 2 -->
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg border border-brand-accent/20 hover:border-brand-accent/50 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3">
            Pattern Tracking
          </h3>

          <p class="text-brand-muted mb-4">
            I track patterns across weeks. Compliance. Excuses. Trends you'd never catch yourself.
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm text-brand-accent font-semibold">
            Data, not vibes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefit 3 -->
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg border border-brand-accent/20 hover:border-brand-accent/50 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3">
            Done-For-You Programming
          </h3>

          <p class="text-brand-muted mb-4">
            Done-for-you nutrition. Training in an app. One strategy call per week. Everything built around your schedule.
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm text-brand-accent font-semibold">
            You execute. I handle the rest.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefit 4 -->
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg border border-brand-accent/20 hover:border-brand-accent/50 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3">
            Accountability With Teeth
          </h3>

          <p class="text-brand-muted mb-4">
            Missed a workout? I'm going to ask why. And when you say "work was busy" I'm going to remind you that work's been busy since 2019. No shame. Just won't let you believe your own bullshit.
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm text-brand-accent font-semibold">
            Kind, not nice. There's a difference.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Benefit 5 -->
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg border border-brand-accent/20 hover:border-brand-accent/50 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3">
            Weekly Strategy Call
          </h3>

          <p class="text-brand-muted mb-4">
            Adjustments, obstacles, what's next. One call per week to keep you on track and evolve the plan as your life changes.
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm text-brand-accent font-semibold">
            Human touch when it matters.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Box -->
        <div class="bg-brand-accent p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Ready to start?
          </h3>

          <button
            class="bg-white text-brand-accent hover:bg-gray-100 font-bold py-3 px-8 text-base transition-all duration-200 mb-4"
            onclick="window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('daisy:open'))"
          >
            Start a quick chat with Daisy, my Client Success Coach
          </button>

          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">
            She'll ask what's not working. Then we'll fix it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
